OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fmostly clear night is expected with
OL,7,Flight winds. It will stay warm for
OL,8,Fmany overnight, and will be feeling
OL,9,Fhumid. Some patchy mist may form, but
OL,10,Flikely dispersing soon after sunrise,
OL,11,Fespecially inland.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FVery warm, perhaps hot in
OL,14,Fplaces, and sunny with light winds.
OL,15,FThe odd patch of low cloud or mist may
OL,16,Fform later along coasts. Warm and
OL,17,Fhumid overnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
