OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FStaying very warm or hot Thursday,
OL,7,Fthough perhaps cooler along cloudier
OL,8,Fcoasts. Warm or hot again Friday with
OL,9,Flong sunny periods, though thundery
OL,10,Fshowers may develop. Cooler with
OL,11,Fshowers Saturday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
